@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Reviewed
Reviewed --> Shipped : reject
Shipped --> Created : review
Shipped : entry / log library
Created --> Rejected : approve
Rejected --> Archived : review
Rejected : entry / log library
Archived --> Active : review
Active --> Reviewed : revert
Active --> [*]
@enduml